days or something,

00:28:59.327 --> 00:29:02.015
right?
So, velocity is 2ÏR/28

00:29:02.015 --> 00:29:03.330
days.
Put it into seconds,

00:29:03.330 --> 00:29:05.099
you get some acceleration.
Yes?

00:29:05.099 --> 00:29:07.020
Student: Are you
assuming that the orbit is a

00:29:07.020 --> 00:29:07.662
